        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1945-07-31T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1945-07-31T00:00:00-05:00" n="1393" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d1393">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">
                    <persName corresp="#p_MS1">Mikołajczyk</persName> Papers</note>
                <head>No. 1393<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Diary Entry by the Polish Deputy Prime Minister</hi>
                        (<persName corresp="#p_MS1">
                        <hi rend="italic">Mikołajczyk</hi>
                    </persName>)<note n="1" xml:id="d1393fn1">Cf. <hi rend="italic">ante</hi>, <ref target="#pg_541">p. 541</ref>.</note>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Translation]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">[<placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Babelsberg</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1945-07-31">July 31,
                            1945</date>.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Mr. <persName corresp="#p_HWA2">Harriman</persName> called in the afternoon.<note n="2" xml:id="d1393fn2">From the discussion which took place toward the end
                        of the Eleventh Plenary Meeting on July 31, it would appear that <persName corresp="#p_HWA2">Harriman</persName> probably paid his call on the
                        Polish Delegation following the adjournment of that meeting at 7:15 p.m. Cf.
                            <hi rend="italic">ante</hi>, <ref target="#pg_527">pp. 527</ref>–<ref target="#pg_528">528</ref>, <ref target="#pg_538">538</ref>.</note> On
                    behalf of President <persName corresp="#p_TJV1">Truman</persName>, as chairman
                    of the meeting of the Big Three which began at 4 o’clock, he invited the Polish
                    Delegation to see President <persName corresp="#p_TJV1">Truman</persName> the
                    next day, when the latter would communicate the results of the meeting
                    today.…</p>
            </div>
        </body>
